7.5 ER Diagram (optional if storage used later)
Entity: Response (response_id, category, text).
________________________________________
8. Design Decisions & Rationale
•	Rule based approach: Chosen for simplicity and clarity in a beginner project.
•	Randomization: Adds variety to responses, making the chatbot feel less repetitive.
•	Multiple personas: Enhances engagement and creativity.
•	Text based interface: Keeps the project lightweight and easy to run.
________________________________________
9. Implementation Details
•	Language: Python 3.x
•	Libraries: random for randomized responses
•	Input/Output: Command line interaction
•	Structure: Lists of responses grouped by intent (greeting, joke, fallback, etc.)
________________________________________
